HEADWORD: Reichsrath
<hw>Reichs"rath`</hw> <pr>(r?ks"r?t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[G]</ety> <def>The parliament of Austria (exclusive of Hungary,
which has its own diet, or parliament). It consists of an Upper and a
Lower House, or a House of Lords and a House of
Representatives.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reichsstand</ent>⟦br⟧
